### Test Contact APIs với API Key
### API Key mặc định: bitrix-oauth-default-key

### 1. Lấy danh sách tất cả contacts
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts?domain=test.bitrix24.com
x-api-key: bitrix-oauth-default-key

### 2. Tìm kiếm contacts theo tên
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts?domain=test.bitrix24.com&name=Nguyễn
x-api-key: bitrix-oauth-default-key

### 3. Tìm kiếm contacts theo email
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts?domain=test.bitrix24.com&email=test@example.com
x-api-key: bitrix-oauth-default-key

### 4. Lấy thông tin contact theo ID
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts/123?domain=test.bitrix24.com
x-api-key: bitrix-oauth-default-key

### 5. Tạo contact mới
POST http://localhost:3000/contacts?domain=test.bitrix24.com
x-api-key: bitrix-oauth-default-key
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nguyễn Văn A",
  "address": {
    "ward": "Phường 1",
    "district": "Quận 1",
    "city": "TP. Hồ Chí Minh"
  },
  "phone": "0123456789",
  "email": "nguyenvana@example.com",
  "website": "https://example.com",
  "bankInfo": {
    "bankName": "Vietcombank",
    "accountNumber": "1234567890"
  }
}

### 6. Cập nhật contact
PUT http://localhost:3000/contacts/123?domain=test.bitrix24.com
x-api-key: bitrix-oauth-default-key
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nguyễn Văn B",
  "phone": "0987654321",
  "email": "nguyenvanb@example.com",
  "bankInfo": {
    "bankName": "Techcombank",
    "accountNumber": "0987654321"
  }
}

### 7. Xóa contact
DELETE http://localhost:3000/contacts/123?domain=test.bitrix24.com
x-api-key: bitrix-oauth-default-key

### 8. Test không có API Key (sẽ trả về 401)
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts?domain=test.bitrix24.com

### 9. Test API Key sai (sẽ trả về 401)
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts?domain=test.bitrix24.com
x-api-key: wrong-api-key
